  })))))))))))), mdx("p", null, "That exponent is a sum of integrals, which is growing. Good luck.")), mdx("p", null, "Defense is a human problem: context, trust, judgment, thankless work over years. Offense is a compute problem: pattern match, generate variants, probe at scale, move on. One of these scales with Moore's law. The other doesn't."), mdx("h2", {
